      "writtenOn": "2021-05-04T23:36:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/main:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/resultdb/internal/invocations/misc.go;l\u003d35;drc\u003dcab3e2fc12192ab1556ed0f3ffc80a897868e2b3\ntells me this runs a query, hence i take it that max shard number may change in the future, and if it does, wouldn\u0027t you want the deadline enforcer to notice new shards?\n\nBtw, how does the rest of ResultDB code handle this?",
      "revId": "1a7dd097e22be52a29edaa7f3396e2fe0bf66954",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
