      "writtenOn": "2021-05-06T00:26:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Actually this could be removed after we finalize the backlog of expired invocations. The only practical limit we should have is the number of rows updated in each transaction, and we are likely to hit that with the backlog.\n\nAh, I see what you mean. As currently set-up we can only finalize 100 invocations per shard per minute. That\u0027s still 167 qps.",
      "parentUuid": "5626f4f9_0b9ed2dc",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 74,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 74,
        "endChar": 11
      },
      "revId": "1a7dd097e22be52a29edaa7f3396e2fe0bf66954",
